Installation
============

1) Download the application:

    $ git clone https://gitlab.bio.crag.local/jjene/tfaviewer.git

2) Install Node.js (https://nodejs.org/es/):

    Linux   : $ sudo apt-get install node
    MacOS X : $ brew install node

3) Install gyp:

	$ npm install -g node-gyp

4) Compile the app:

    $ ./compile.sh


Launch the T-Fasta Viewer
=========================

1) Run:

	$ ./start_viewer.sh

2) Open:

    http://localhost:8082


Stop the T-Fasta Viewer
=======================

1) Run:

	$ ./stop_viewer.sh


Troubleshooting
===============

*) Problem: ./start_viewer.sh shows "Error: listen EADDRINUSE"
   Solution: change the port number in the server.js file: server.listen(8082);


